śrutacintābhāvanāmayaprajñāpariniṣṭhitaṃ vastu na smaraṇam adhivasati. tanmūlaṃ ca sarvaṃ kalyāṇam. kim iva? yathā sacchidrakumbhe mukhanikśiptam udakam adhastād gacchati nāvatiṣṭhate.

<commentary>idam aparaṃ tadvayatireke dūṣaṇam āha.

bahavo 'pi bahuśrutāḥ tathā śraddhāvanto yatnaparāḥ śikṣāyām ādarakāriṇaḥ asaṃprajanyadoṣeṇa āpattikaluṣitā bhavanti kāyacittapracārāpratyavekṣaṇāt.</commentary>